{"tid":47293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係幾年前，我同一個寡婦結左婚","createTime":"2016-12-20T08:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T10:02:39.000Z","uid":17378,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42ae300723b2e7747805a24d1915dd8716d272e8","tid":47293,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"係幾年前，我同一個寡婦結左婚，佢有一個已成年既女，後來嫁左比我老豆。&nbsp;<br />\n咁我繼女就做左我後媽，而我老豆就做左我女婿。&nbsp;<br />\n兩年後我老婆同我生左一個仔，佢係我後媽既同母異父既細路，我個仔叫我「老豆」，我就叫我個仔「舅父」。&nbsp;<br />\n...我繼女又為我老豆生左一個仔，佢係我細佬，但佢又要叫我外公。&nbsp;<br />\n我係我老婆個老公，但係我老婆係我後媽個阿媽喎，&nbsp;<br />\n所以我係自己既外公。&nbsp;<br />\n到左新年，黎料啦，&nbsp;<br />\n我就同我後媽同我老豆，即係同我繼女同女婿交換利是，&nbsp;<br />\n又同我個仔，即係我舅父交換，我封廿蚊比佢，丫佢竟然封張一百蚊比我，真係多謝舅父!&nbsp;<br />\n講到我細佬，我都唔知封唔封比佢好，冇理由阿哥比利是細佬架...但係心諗我又係佢外公，所以都係比左十蚊佢買野食算數。&nbsp;<br />\n食團年飯果陣，我係抬面上面放左一封利是，再拎返封利是上手，叫左聲 :「多謝外公!」"},{"pid":"ab775530f8065e06ed0518cc00b7ac638c85d5cc","tid":47293,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"6434f227e82b97e6bd2bb544d872c41950d3de24","tid":47293,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa1d925da5170ebc5add43f434cebf54620337f","tid":47293,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2f2266c735e68339b7bcf318c5a0b1739518a1","tid":47293,"uid":46121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3bb156af8ef150e0928634819a6e730acc93f843","tid":47293,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f155b38fd3224e9266c5fac6f10ff57841a5c3ea","tid":47293,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6863e85324db8f76299970f34defa438d9ab7ec6","tid":47293,"uid":26047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"又試新會員好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df98edf929b55aba2a1f7bf339822588e8c0d364","tid":47293,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"冇試新會員嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好文不妨一睇再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd20a0fe360009593b9514281048f52a66c3f56","tid":47293,"uid":64663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88426516ecf4b7a985951a134ea34f87fcf0953e","tid":47293,"uid":37752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:36:30.000Z","msg":"more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021a7ff4bfa6238f6695709de3b38e93241bd7c5","tid":47293,"uid":64045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504a7f9ec37cd0b39d65b64bf69a575d3ef8085d","tid":47293,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}